Project Overview

AI Content Studio is an automation designed to eliminate repetitive content writing.

Instead of manually creating content for every platform, the workflow takes one topic from Google Sheets and automatically generates optimized content for:

LinkedIn
Instagram
X (Twitter)
TikTok
YouTube Shorts
Hook
Call-to-Action
Hashtags

The generated content is then written back into Google Sheets automatically.

🎯 Goal

Reduce hours of manual content creation into a fully automated workflow using AI.

