🧠 AI Prompt

The AI receives one topic and returns structured JSON.

Example:

{
  "hook":"...",
  "linkedin":"...",
  "instagram":"...",
  "x":"...",
  "tiktok":"...",
  "youtube":"...",
  "hashtags":"...",
  "cta":"..."
}
💻 JavaScript Parser

The JavaScript node converts the AI response into separate fields that Google Sheets can understand.

Example:

const ai = JSON.parse($json.aiResponse);

return [{
  json:{
    HOOK: ai.hook,
    LINKEDIN: ai.linkedin,
    INSTAGRAM: ai.instagram,
    X: ai.x,
    TIKTOK: ai.tiktok,
    "YOUTUBE SHORTS": ai.youtube,
    HASHTAGS: ai.hashtags,
    CTA: ai.cta
  }
}];
🔄 Workflow Process
Read Topic from Google Sheets
Loop through each pending row
Send topic to OpenAI
AI generates content
Parse JSON response
Update Google Sheets
Mark row as Generated
